  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-06-11",
    "date": "2026-03-30T15:51:45Z",
    "text": "This resolution recognizes the historic significance of the 127th anniversary of the Philippines' sovereignty and independence.\n\nThe resolution also (1) reaffirms the bonds of friendship and cooperation between the United States and the Philippines, (2) recognizes the courage and bravery of Filipino and Filipino American\u00a0servicemembers who have fought alongside and in the U.S. armed forces, and (3) supports the recognition of Philippines Independence Day."
  },
